name: Vittorio Lanni
coverLetter: My name is Vittorio Lanni, I'm from west palm beach florida and have just moved to Santa Monica. Im 20 years old and I've been smoking weed for about 4 years now. i was looking at jobs and i saw this and new this would be perfect. weed is a beautiful plant and a beautiful thing and id love to learn and work with the plant as much as i could.
